{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_06_01_short",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 実家に来る？ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――大阪、合同カウントダウンライブ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The joint countdown live at Osaka",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんな、沢山のエール\nありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To all the fans‚\nthank you so much for the many cheers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "今年最後のステージを、こうしてみんなと\n迎えることが出来て、私達は幸せです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're happy that we could spend the last stage\nof this year with everyone like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ、はぁ、良かった。無事だったんだな\n莉央さんが来ないって聞いた時は驚いたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huff‚ huff. I'm relieved. You're safe.\nI was surprised when I heard you weren't coming‚ Rio-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それから……今更だけど、遅刻してごめんなさい\n遅刻は、この後のパフォーマンスで挽回します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… It's late to say this now‚ but I'm sorry for being late.\nI'll make up for it with my performance afterward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "精一杯、みんなのために歌うから聴いて下さい！\n『最高優美ロンリネス』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll sing my heart out for everyone!\n\"Saiko-yuubi Loneliness\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1,
      "sfxList": [
